@page
@model WebApplication1.Pages.AboutUsModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script:wght@400..700&family=Pacifico&family=Playfair+Display+SC:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400;1,700;1,900&family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&family=Sigmar&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/AboutUs.css"/>
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="aboutContainer">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
        <h3>Welcome to Balay Na Homes – where comfort meets community!</h3>
        <p>Balay Na Homes was created to provide our homeowners with a safe, accessible, and functional space that fosters a strong sense of belonging within the neighborhood.</p>
        <p>At Balay Na Homes, we are dedicated to crafting a harmonious environment for homeowners who seek peace, connection, and quality living. Our mission is to create more than just homes; we are building a vibrant and thriving community where families can grow, connect, and truly belong.</p>
        <p>We believe that a home is not just a place – it’s a sanctuary where memories are made, relationships are nurtured, and lives are enriched. That’s why every aspect of our subdivision system is designed with care, ensuring that each space reflects our commitment to comfort, peace, and togetherness.</p>
        <p>Whether you are looking for your first home, a space to retire in, or a place to raise a family, Balay Na Homes offers a welcoming environment for everyone. Our focus is on building homes that not only meet your needs but also foster a strong sense of community, making it easier for neighbors to connect and support one another.</p>
        <p>Join us at Balay Na Homes and experience a lifestyle where every detail is crafted for comfort, peace, and a sense of belonging.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

